Package: streamgraph
Type: Package
Title: Streaming (Dynamic) Graph Analytics
Version: 0.1.0.9002
Date: 2026-07-01
Authors@R: person("bagol1000", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "01199218@pw.edu.pl")
Description: Maintains graph metrics incrementally as edges arrive in a stream.
    Provides an in-memory dynamic graph with incremental connected components
    (Union-Find), triangle counting, degree tracking, neighbourhood queries and
    approximate betweenness, backed by a 'C++17' core with 'OpenMP' support.
    Node IDs are 0-indexed.
